                                  \n                          \n\n\n                            <div class=\"teacher-content\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/dynclicks.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/jquery/jquery-latest.min.js\"></script>\n<div class=\"teacher-details\">\n                                    <div class=\"teacher-basic\">\n\n\n<div class=\"teacher-basic-inner\">\n    <img src=\"/__local/1/CB/05/C5F42F01A61EC96B4140E57935E_5B46E5DC_42AB9.jpg\">\n    <div class=\"teacher-basic-data\">\n    <p class=\"teacher-basic-name\">陈熹</p>\n    <div id=\"desc\"><p>副研究员</p></div>   \n     <script>  \n   String.prototype.html = function(encode) {\n    var replace =[\"&#39;\", \"'\", \"&quot;\", '\"', \"&nbsp;\", \" \", \"&gt;\", \">\", \"&lt;\", \"<\", \"&yen;\", \"¥\", \"&amp;\", \"&\"];    \n    var replaceReverse = [\"&amp;\", \"&\", \"¥\", \"&yen;\", \"&lt;\", \"<\", \"&gt;\", \">\", \"&nbsp;\", \" \", \"&quot;\", '\"', \"&#39;\", \"'\"];\n      var target;\n      if (encode) {\n        target = replaceReverse;\n      } else {\n        target = replace;\n      }\n    for (var i=0,str=this;i< target.length;i+= 2) {\n       str=str.replace(new RegExp(target[i],'g'),target[i+1]);\n    }\n    return str;\n  };\n  var  zzz =\"&lt;p&gt;副研究员&lt;/p&gt;\";\n  \n\n\ndocument.getElementById('desc').innerHTML=zzz.html(true);\n\n             </script> \n    \n    \n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"teacher-basic-sns\">\n        <p><img src=\"../../dfiles/5167/env/images/email.jpg\">邮箱：chenx101@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n        <p><img src=\"../../dfiles/5167/env/images/phone.jpg\">电话：</p>\n        <p><img src=\"../../dfiles/5167/env/images/location.jpg\">地点：清华大学环境学院437室</p>\n    </div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n  \n<div class=\"teacher-details-message\">\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\"><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper1.jpg\"><p>教育背景</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p>2006.08 — 2010.07 清华大学环境学院，给排水科学与工程专业，学士</p>\n<p>2007.08 — 2010.07 清华大学经济管理学院，经济学专业（双学位），学士</p>\n<p>2010.08 — 2016.07 清华大学环境学院，环境科学与工程专业，博士（硕博连读）</p>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: none;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper2.jpg\"><p>工作履历</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content teacher-hidden\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p>2022.07 — 至今 清华大学环境学院 副研究员</p>\n<p>2020.01 — 2022.05 美国普林斯顿大学土木与环境工程系 副研究员</p>\n<p>2018.09 — 2019.12 美国普林斯顿大学土木与环境工程系 博士后</p>\n<p>2016.10 — 2018.08 美国科罗拉多大学博尔德分校 博士后</p>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: block;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper3.jpg\"><p>学术兼职</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">IWA 中国青年委员会委员</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">担任环境、能源与材料领域十余本高水平期刊审稿人，包括<em>Environmental Science &amp; Technology</em>, <em>Water Research</em>等</p>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: none;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper4.jpg\"><p>研究领域</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content teacher-hidden\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">从事面向“碳中和”的水-能源-资源耦联新方法及技术体系研究。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">具体方向包括：1）战略高值金属离子提取与回收，2）三维蒸发材料研究及过程优化，3）界面结晶过程与物质分离，4）工业废水资源化与零排放</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">课题组长期招聘具有环境、材料、化学、化工等研究背景的博士后，支持申报“国家资助博士后研究人员计划”（含“博新计划”）、“清华大学博士后海外引才专项”、清华大学“水木学者”计划和青年基金等，有意向者请将简历和代表性成果发送至<a href=\"mailto:chenx101@tsinghua.edu.cn\">chenx101@tsinghua.edu.cn</a></p>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: block;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper5.jpg\"><p>研究概况</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content teacher-hidden\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">基于三维蒸发梯度结晶的工业废水锂回收新工艺研究，国家基金委面上项目，2024-2027，项目负责人.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">基于三维结晶法的退役锂电池资源回收新工艺研究，地方政府科研项目，2025-2026项目负责人.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">臭氧氧化联动提升工业废水处理MBR工艺开发课题，企事业委托项目，2022-2025.11.08，课题技术负责人.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">膜技术在特种分子筛生产废水中的应用研究，企事业委托项目，2024-2025，项目负责人.</p></li>\n</ol>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: block;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper6.jpg\"><p>荣誉与奖励</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content teacher-hidden\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p>2020 ISMET Innovation Award</p>\n<p>2018 教育部自然科学奖一等奖（5/9）</p>\n<p>2018 <em>Environmental Science: Water Research &amp; Technology</em>-最佳论文奖</p>\n<p>2017 <em>Water Research</em>优秀审稿人</p>\n<p>2016 北京市优秀博士毕业生</p>\n<p>2016 清华大学“紫荆学者”称号</p>\n<p>2016 清华大学优秀博士毕业生</p>\n<p>2016 清华大学优秀博士论文</p>\n<p>2016 清华大学“马约翰”奖</p>\n<p>2016 美国Boeing奖学金</p>\n<p>2015 全国高等学校给排水相关专业在校生研究成果展示会- 最佳论文金奖</p>\n<p>2015 首都高校女子足球联赛冠军</p>\n<p>2013 国家奖学金</p>\n<p>2013 清华大学“林枫辅导员”奖</p>\n<p>2012 清华大学特等奖学金</p>\n<p>2012 美国The Dow可持续发展创新挑战赛- 特等奖</p>\n<p>2011 清华大学优秀学生干部</p>\n<p>2010 首都高校秋季学生田径运动会甲组女子跳高冠军、女子4 ˣ 100接力冠军</p>\n<p>本科阶段（2006~2010） 清华大学本科优秀毕业论文；清华大学社会实践学生标兵；全国环境友好科技竞赛实物类第一名；清华大学“挑战杯”学生课外科技创新竞赛一等奖；清华大学能源动力设计大赛一等奖；清华大学马约翰杯田径运动会女子三项全能冠军（连续十年，打破纪录）、女子4ˣ100米接力冠军（连续十年）、女子篮球联赛总冠军、女子足球联赛总冠军，保持多项校、院竞赛记录</p>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: block;\">展开</button></div><div class=\"teacher-details-part\"><div class=\"teacher-part-title\"><img src=\"https://www.env.tsinghua.edu.cn/dfiles/5167/env/images/paper7.jpg\"><p>学术成果</p></div><div class=\"teacher-part-content teacher-hidden\"><div class=\"teacher-part-content-hidden\"><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">截至2024年12月，在环境、能源、材料等相关领域期刊发表论文40余篇，代表性论文发表于Nature Water（封面论文）, Energy &amp; Environmental Science（封面论文*2）及Advanced Materials等国际顶级期刊。Google论文总引超过3200次，H指数为32。</p>\n<p><strong>一、代表性期刊论文（<sup>*</sup>通讯作者；<sup>#</sup> 共同一作）：</strong></p>\n<ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.<sup>#</sup></strong>, Yang, M.<sup>#</sup>, Zheng, S., Temprano-Coleto, F., Qi Dong; Cheng, G., Yao, N., Stone, H., Hu, L., Ren, Z.J<sup>*</sup>. Spatially separated crystallization for selective lithium extraction from saline water. <em>Nature Water</em>, 2023, 1, 808-817. （封面文章）</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, He, S., Falinski, M., Wang, Y., Li, T., Zheng, S., Sun, D., Dai, J., Bian, Y., Zhu, X., Jiang, J., Hu, L.<sup>*</sup>, and Ren, Z.J<sup>*</sup>. (2021). Sustainable zero liquid discharge of concentrated brine by Janus wood evaporator. <em>Energy &amp; Environmental Science</em>, 2021, 14(10): 5347-5357. (封面文章, 高被引论文, 2021 EES热点论文)</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sun, D., Bian, Y., Liu, P., Wang, Han, Xu, T., Zhang, X., Liang, P., Ren, Z. J., <strong>Chen, X.<sup>*</sup></strong>, and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2021). Electricity enhances biological Fe(III) reduction and phosphorus recovery from FeP complex: proof of concept and kinetic analysis. <em>ACS ES&amp;T Engineering</em>. 2021, 1, 3, 523–532. （封面文章）.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.<sup>#</sup></strong>, Zhu, X.<sup>#</sup>, He, S., Hu, L. &amp; Ren, Z. J.<sup>*</sup> (2020). Advanced nanowood materials for the water-energy nexus. <em>Advanced Materials</em>, 2001240, 2020.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Lobo, F. L., Bian, Y., Lu, L., Chen, X., Tucker, M. P., Wang, Y., Ren, Z. J.<sup>*</sup> (2020), Electrical decoupling of microbial electrochemical reactions enables spontaneous H2 evolution. <em>Energy &amp; Environmental Science</em> 13,495-502. (封面文章, 2020 EES热点论文).</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Katahira, R., Ge, Z., Lu, L., Hou, D., Peterson, D.J., Tucker, M.P., Chen, X.<sup>*</sup>, and Ren, Z.J<sup>*</sup>. (2019). Microbial electrochemical treatment of biorefinery black liquor and resource recovery. <em>Green Chemistry</em> 21, 1258-1266. (封面文章).</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sun, D., Gao, Y., Hou, D., Zuo, K., <strong>Chen, X.<sup>*</sup></strong>, Liang, P., Zhang, X., Ren, Z.J., and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2018). Energy-neutral sustainable nutrient recovery incorporated with the wastewater purification process in an enlarged microbial nutrient recovery cell. <em>Journal of Power Sources</em>, 384, 160-164.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gao, Y., Sun, D., Wang, H., Lu, L., Ma, H., Wang, L., Ren, Z.J., Liang, P., Zhang, X., <strong>Chen, X.<sup>*</sup></strong>, and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2018). Urine-powered synergy of nutrient recovery and urine purification in a microbial electrochemical system. <em>Environmental Science: Water Research &amp; Technology</em> 4, 1427-1438. (封面文章，2018最佳论文).</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Zhou, H., Zuo, K., Zhou, Y., Wang, Q., Sun, D., Gao, Y., Liang, P., Zhang, X.<sup>*</sup>, Ren, Z.J., Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2017). Self-sustaining advanced wastewater purification and simultaneous in situ nutrient recovery in a novel bioelectrochemical system. <em>Chemical Engineering Journal</em>, 330, 692-697.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.<sup>#</sup></strong>, Gao, Y.<sup>#</sup>, Hou, D., Ma, H., Lu, L., Sun, D., Zhang, X., Liang, P., Huang, X.<sup>*</sup>, and Ren, Z.J<sup>*</sup>. (2017). The Microbial electrochemical current accelerates area hydrolysis for recovery of nutrients from source-separated urine. <em>Environmental Science &amp; Technology Letters</em>, 4, 305-310.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Sun, H., Liang, P., Zhang, X.<sup>*</sup>, and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2016). Optimization of membrane stack configuration in enlarged microbial desalination cells for efficient water desalination. <em>Journal of Power Sources</em>, 324, 79-85.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Liang, P., Zhang, X., and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2016). Bioelectrochemical systems-driven directional ion transport enables low-energy water desalination, pollutant removal, and resource recovery. <em>Bioresource Technology</em>, 215, 274-284.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Sun, D., Zhang, X.<sup>*</sup>, Liang, P., and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2015). Novel self-driven microbial nutrient recovery cell with simultaneous wastewater purification. <em>Science Reports</em>, 5.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Liang, P., Wei, Z.M., Zhang, X.Y., and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2012). Sustainable water desalination and electricity generation in a separator coupled stacked microbial desalination cell with buffer free electrolyte circulation. <em>Bioresource Technology</em>, 119, 88-93.</p></li>\n <li><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Chen, X.</strong>, Xia, X., Liang, P., Cao, X., Sun, H., and Huang, X<sup>*</sup>. (2011). Stacked microbial desalination cells to enhance water desalination efficiency. <em>Environmental Science &amp; Technology</em>, 45, 2465-2470.</p></li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>二、专著</strong></p>\n<ol class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n <li><p>《水处理工程物理化学技术》, 黄霞, 张潇源, <strong>陈熹</strong>. 高等教育出版社, 2025.</p></li>\n</ol>\n<p><br></p><p><br></p>  </div></div><button class=\"teacher-part-content-more\" style=\"display: block;\">展开</button></div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n</div>\n    \n   \n \n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n</div>\n                           \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n         <!-- 尾部 -->\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <div class=\"footer-content\">\n                <div class=\"friend-link\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/openlink.js\"></script>\n<h3><span>友情</span>链接</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1673105411, 61520)\">清华大学</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://www.thunel.com/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1673105411, 61522)\">大气污染物与温室气体协同控制国家工程研究中心</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://cwe.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1673105411, 82738)\">清华大学水质与水生态研究中心</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://www.tsinghua-riet.com/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1673105411, 61523)\">清华苏州环境创新研究院</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"http://journal.hep.com.cn/fese/EN/2095-2201/home.shtml\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;,